280
00:25:05,491 --> 00:25:07,131
  W-What did you say?  

281
00:25:07,131 --> 00:25:08,861
Who did?

282
00:25:13,191 --> 00:25:14,941
 Is it ready? 

283
00:25:14,941 --> 00:25:19,181
 I'll do it since I'm instructed to do so. But she might really die from it. 

284
00:25:19,181 --> 00:25:21,801
 Right. That's the whole point. 

285
00:25:21,801 --> 00:25:27,521
