294
00:26:06,511 --> 00:26:08,121
I bet it was all part of the plan.

295
00:26:08,121 --> 00:26:09,571
Who? Who? Who?

296
00:26:09,571 --> 00:26:11,491
I have to find that out.

297
00:26:11,491 --> 00:26:14,201
When the audition ends tomorrow, I'll go to the police station with Miss.

