314
00:27:51,701 --> 00:27:53,431
That's no use.

315
00:27:53,431 --> 00:27:56,221
Can you just kill everyone like Director Ji's interpretation?

316
00:27:56,221 --> 00:28:00,531
That's more intense. You really have to win tomorrow.

